Package org.hms.services.drugdispensary

Class DrugInventoryEntry

java.lang.Object
org.hms.entities.AbstractTableEntry
org.hms.services.drugdispensary.DrugInventoryEntry
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class DrugInventoryEntry extends AbstractTableEntry
The DrugInventoryEntry class represents an entry in a drug inventory table. It includes details such as the name of the drug, its current stock quantity, and a threshold value for triggering low stock alerts.
